程序包 main.utils.exception

package main.utils.exception
  • 异常错误
    类
    说明
    ModelAlreadyExistsException
    The ModelAlreadyExistsException class is a custom exception that is thrown when an attempt is made to add a model to a repository that already contains a model with the same ID.
    ModelNotFoundException
    The ModelNotFoundException class is a custom exception that is thrown when a requested model cannot be found in a repository.
    PageBackException
    The PageBackException class is a custom exception that is thrown when a user attempts to navigate back from a UI page where it is not allowed.
    PasswordIncorrectException
    The PasswordIncorrectException class represents an exception that is thrown when a password entered by the user is incorrect.
